  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Le Sherpa is on a half board basis. </p>
<p>The hotel has a really good reputation for the cuisine with use of regional productions and chef's specialities. Each morning a continental buffet breakfast with additional hot options is served between 7.45-9.30am (subject to change).</p>
<p>When you have returned from a day on the slopes, you can enjoy a five course evening meals with choice of menu including soup, starter, main, cheese and dessert courses. Twice a week there is a local speciality evening which can include raclette or fondue. Earlier meal times for children are available (on request)</p>
<p>Special dietary requirements can be catered for (vegetarian and vegans). Gluten free diets can be catered for but a supplement may be charged locally</p>
<p>Christmas &amp; New Year gala dinners included</p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
